          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-15621 wbc: free buffer when batched RPC is committed",
        "message": "LU-15621 wbc: free buffer when batched RPC is committed\n\nAdd test srcipt sanity-wbc.sh test_106 for replay recovery of the\nbatched RPC.\n\nIt should not free the registered buffer for bulk I/O upon the\nreply of the batched RPC. It should be in the commit callback,\ncalled when request is committed and about to be freed.\nOtherwise, it will cause the replay recovery failure.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I4735ceef696ef8284d5db202a072e33b0b609851\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
